{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"<mphantom>","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mphantom","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","hasMathML":true,"sidebarHTML":"\n    <ol>\n        <li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element\">MathML Referenz</a></strong>\n\n        \n            </li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/maction\">&lt;maction&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/math\">&lt;math&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/menclose\">&lt;menclose&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/merror\">&lt;merror&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfenced\">&lt;mfenced&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfrac\">&lt;mfrac&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mi\">&lt;mi&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mn\">&lt;mn&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mover\">&lt;mover&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mpadded\">&lt;mpadded&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mphantom\">&lt;mphantom&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mroot\">&lt;mroot&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/ms\">&lt;ms&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msqrt\">&lt;msqrt&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstyle\">&lt;mstyle&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msub\">&lt;msub&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msubsup\">&lt;msubsup&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msup\">&lt;msup&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\">&lt;mtable&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtd\">&lt;mtd&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtext\">&lt;mtext&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtr\">&lt;mtr&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munder\">&lt;munder&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munderover\">&lt;munderover&gt;</a></li>\n        \n\n        \n    </ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p class=\"summary\">Das <code>&lt;mphantom&gt;</code>-Element in MathML wird nicht dargestellt, nimmt aber den Platz ein, als wenn es dargestellt würde. (engl. phantom = Trugbild, Erscheinung)</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"attribute","title":"Attribute","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"attr-class-id-style\">class, id, style</dt>\n <dd>Zur Einbindung von <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS\">CSS-Stylesheets</a> und zur direkten Anwendung von CSS-Angaben.</dd>\n <dt id=\"attr-mathbackground\">mathbackground</dt>\n <dd>Die Hintergrundfarbe. Folgende Notationen sind erlaubt: <code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/Farben#rgb()\">#rgb</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/Farben#rgb()\">#rrggbb</a></code> und <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/Farben#Werte\">HTML-Farbnamen</a>.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiele","title":"Beispiele","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Beispiel: <img alt=\"x+  z\" src=\"/files/3199/mphantom.png\" style=\"margin-left: 10px; vertical-align: middle;\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n\n<p>Darstellung in Deinem Browser: <math> <mrow> <mi> x </mi> <mo> + </mo> <mphantom> <mi> y </mi> <mo> + </mo> </mphantom> <mi> z </mi> </mrow> </math></p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>math</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mrow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> x <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> + <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mphantom</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> y <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> + <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mphantom</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> z <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mrow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>math</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Standard</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Bemerkung</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/MathML3/chapter3.html#presm.mphantom\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">MathML 3.0<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'mphantom' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Empfehlung</span></td>\n   <td>Current specification</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/MathML2/chapter3.html#presm.mphantom\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">MathML 2.0<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'mphantom' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Empfehlung</span></td>\n   <td>Initial specification</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browserkompatibilität","title":"Browserkompatibilität","isH3":false,"content":"<